fr.inria.atlanmod.mogwai.datastore

Interface ModelDatastore<D,E,R,A>

  • Type Parameters:
    D - the type of the data source to use
    E - the type representing model elements
    R - the type representing references
    A - the type representing attributes' value
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    PipesDatastore<D,E,R,A>
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    NeoEMFGraphDatastore

    public interface ModelDatastore<D,E,R,A>
    Defines the methods that should be implemented to manipulate a data source as a model.

    The methods defined in this interface are called within the generated scripts and are responsible of retrieving EMF-related information inside a data source. They are inspired from the ones defined in the ATL API.

    This mapping provides a low-level API to manipulate the model. It can be combined with other mappings such as to provide a rich model navigation API depending developer's needs.

    A custom ModelDatastore can be provided to the Mogwai engine using the following code: 

     
 ModelMapping mapping = new // an implementation of this interface
 
 MogwaiQuery query = Mogwai(ATL)QueryBuilder.newBuilder()
 	.fromFile(new File(<file containing the query to execute>))
 	.bind(ModelMapping.BINDING_NAME, mapping)
 	.build();
    Author:
    Gwendal DANIEL

      • newInstance

        E newInstance(String typeName,
              String typePackageNsURI,
              String resourceName)
        Creates a new element of the type typeName and add it to the resource resourceName.

        typePackageNsURI can be provided for mappings that support metaclasses defined in multiple EPackages.

        resourceName is optional and can be used by mapping implementation that supports multiple resource in a single database.

        Parameters:
        typeName - the name of the metaclass to create an instance of
        typePackageNsURI - the URI of the EPackage that defines the metaclass typeName
        resourceName - the name of the resource where the new element is stored
        Returns:
        an Object representing the created instance of typeName
